posts.title: I may not be an american, but you guys HAVE to win.
posts.content:
Vote, make sure you spread the message to family, friend, acquaintances, everybody and their grandma in short. Like others say, act like you're losing by 20 points and this can't be said often enough!!! Be the inspiring beacon for conservatives worldwide!

While I'm not from the US, I do fully support the MAGA movement and the values it's centred around (and they should apply for the whole civilized world if you ask me). We also have elections here soon (Romania), 3 consecutive weeks of elections in fact. I don't think it's too much of a stretch to say that a massive victory for you guys would help boost our own based movements. We have our own work to do, but we'd love to see a big victory for Trump.

Keep your eyes on them 24/7 and keep stressing the urgent need to vote on everyone else you know that's on the right side until they actually vote. Don't stop out of politeness, everything is at stake here so keep pressing 'till it's done. There are no excuses this time.

Godspeed and I will be rooting for you all! I'd wish you the best of luck, but the best kind of luck is the one you forge yourself, so go do that!
